  "content": [
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-8120-9fb7-d2956b9833cc",
      "type": "heading_1",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Academic Performance Overview"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81e9-9764-c5e0a14583e4",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "This semester, our student volunteers have not only dedicated countless hours to community service but have also excelled academically. Their ability to juggle these responsibilities showcases remarkable time management and prioritization skills. Below are highlights from a few standout students:"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-815f-a6ac-ffe79064acc8",
      "type": "heading_3",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Emma Thompson:"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81c3-95ce-f8437322830f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**Major:** Biology"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-8187-b412-dc1ea25467ba",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**GPA:** 3.9"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81d9-a220-d1ec96da0a08",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**Notable Courses:**"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81c7-b000-e2270b3bbef6",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Genetics (A)"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-811b-a168-ce86a5210b07",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Organic Chemistry II (A-)"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-814b-9712-e910fce16b1c",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Biostatistics (A)"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-815b-ae79-c5dbfe6b2684",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**Professor's Note:**"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81b8-822b-e1b6914d1aae",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Emma has consistently demonstrated a keen understanding of complex topics, often contributing insightful observations during lectures. Her participation in the Genetics research project was particularly commendable."
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-8181-ba99-e3d945f271f2",
      "type": "heading_3",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Liam Johnson:"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81a0-8160-fe8e4a07e467",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**Major:** Environmental Science"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81d7-a6ea-eda1ba12bc4d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**GPA:** 3.85"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-811c-a4ce-eac5f6c6728a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**Notable Courses:**"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81be-9038-da097c436450",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Climate Change Solutions (A)"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81f9-9f9f-ce9aca169ee9",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Environmental Policy (A-)"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-819d-a815-f6d5a5f4d519",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Ecology (B+)"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-8129-8296-e42491d84efa",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**Professor's Note:**"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81ce-a25c-e486c4e3bebb",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Liam's engagement in class discussions and his leadership in group projects stand out. He successfully led a workshop on sustainable practices at our local community center as part of his volunteer work."
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-8179-8db5-fb38186db8f5",
      "type": "heading_3",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Sophia Martinez:"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81d7-b29b-f8fd8f49747f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**Major:** Computer Science"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-8186-9859-dbaf00783af7",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**GPA:** 4.0"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81a3-bdcf-cafff89940c7",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**Notable Courses:**"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-8147-b502-d4ebe2738543",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Algorithms (A)"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-810d-b1b0-c527d8396c15",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Database Systems (A)"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81b3-a7ed-f8e360d4216a",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Software Engineering (A)"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-8146-bf6a-cc880190b025",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**Professor's Note:**"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81b2-b4fb-f614a00bcd5f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Sophia has excelled in her coursework, often going above and beyond on assignments. She has also been tutoring fellow students in coding, displaying both her knowledge and commitment to volunteerism."
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-813b-ba8d-c2a46a2d50a4",
      "type": "heading_3",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Noah Kim:"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-8146-a950-df02469624f6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**Major:** English Literature"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81b2-8d3c-d403493bf9a5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**GPA:** 3.8"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-819c-a0a4-ee5c06ff682c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**Notable Courses:**"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81b1-88d1-f9499d8a9f02",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Modern American Literature (A-)"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-8166-b0ee-d89e686d4a24",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Creative Writing (A)"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-8189-84fb-fdabb5aca508",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Literary Theory (B+)"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-8140-b151-da0c44df4133",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "**Professor's Note:**"
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-81a6-8e19-ed9f9def19a3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "Noah's critical essays have been a highlight of the semester, showing deep analytical skills and creativity. He has volunteered to organize a series of poetry readings for the local community, blending his academic interests with service."
    },
    {
      "id": "2180dc8f-a0db-813e-a415-ea52f270c9be",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "created_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-20T23:10:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "These students exemplify the dual commitment to academic excellence and community service. Their grades and professors' notes reflect not only their intellectual capabilities but also their leadership, initiative, and the ability to impact positively on those around them."
    }
  ]
